      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节团圆·新疆葵花籽</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        color: #333;\n    }\n    section, footer {\n        padding: 40px 20px;\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: auto;\n    }\n    #hero-banner {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 80px 20px;\n    }\n    #hero-banner h1 {\n        font-size: 2.5rem;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    #hero-banner p {\n        font-size: 1.2rem;\n    }\n    #product-details {\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        border-bottom: 4px solid #FFCC00;\n    }\n    #product-details h2 {\n        color: #D32F2F;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #product-details p {\n        font-size: 1rem;\n        color: #555;\n    }\n    #festival-story {\n        background-color: #FFCC00;\n        color: #D32F2F;\n    }\n    #festival-story h2 {\n        font-size: 1.8rem;\n        margin-bottom: 15px;\n    }\n    #festival-story p {\n        font-size: 1rem;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    #benefits {\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n    }\n    #benefits h2 {\n        color: #8BC34A;\n        margin-bottom: 15px;\n    }\n    #benefits ul {\n        list-style-type: disc;\n        padding-left: 20px;\n        color: #555;\n    }\n    #purchase-cta {\n        text-align: center;\n        background-color: #8BC34A;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n    }\n    #purchase-cta button {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        border: none;\n        padding: 15px 30px;\n        font-size: 1.2rem;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n        border-radius: 5px;\n    }\n    #purchase-cta button:hover {\n        background-color: #b71c1c;\n    }\n    #reviews {\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n    }\n    #reviews h2 {\n        color: #D32F2F;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    #reviews div {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .review-card {\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        padding: 20px;\n        flex: 1 1 calc(33.333% - 20px);\n        box-sizing: border-box;\n        border-radius: 5px;\n    }\n    footer {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    footer p {\n        margin: 5px 0;\n        font-size: 0.9rem;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n        .review-card {\n            flex: 1 1 100%;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<section id=\"hero-banner\">\n    <h1>春节团圆好味道 · 新疆葵花籽</h1>\n    <p>围炉夜话，嗑香葵花籽，分享暖心年味，承载家的味道。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"product-details\">\n    <h2>优选新疆原产葵花籽 · 500g/袋</h2>\n    <p>¥19.9 / 袋 · 精选阳光充沛产地，颗粒饱满，天然健康。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"festival-story\">\n    <h2>瓜子与团圆的故事</h2>\n    <p>在除夕的夜晚，一家人围坐在炭火旁，笑声与葵花籽的香味交织成最温暖的节日画卷。嗑瓜子不仅是味觉享受，更是亲情与乡愁的纽带。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"benefits\">\n    <h2>产品优势</h2>\n    <ul>\n        <li>低温烘焙保留更多营养</li>\n        <li>新疆原产地直供，颗粒饱满</li>\n        <li>小包装随时享用，便于储存</li>\n    </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"purchase-cta\">\n    <button>立即购买</button>\n    <p>春节特惠 · 下单即享包邮配送</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"reviews\">\n    <h2>用户好评</h2>\n    <div>\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <p>颗粒大又香，年夜饭时家人都爱嗑。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <p>包装精致，送礼很体面，味道纯正。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"review-card\">\n            <p>物流很快，收到时瓜子香气扑鼻。</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>\n\n<footer id=\"footer-info\">\n    <p>联系方式：400-123-4567 · 服务时间：9:00-18:00</p>\n    <p>全国包邮 · 破损免费退换保障</p>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
